'''菲茨羅維亞'''（Fitzrovia，{{IPAc-en|f|ɪ|t|s|ˈ|r|əʊ|v|ɪ|ə}}<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/fitzrovia?showCookiePolicy=true|title=Fitzrovia|accessdate=24 September 2014|work=Collins Dictionary|date=n.d.|archive-date=2016-03-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303230950/http://www.collinsdictionary.com/dictionary/english/fitzrovia?showCookiePolicy=true|dead-url=no}}</ref>）是位於[[倫敦市中心|倫敦市中心]]的一個地區，部分屬於[[西敏市|西敏市]]，部分則屬於[[康登倫敦自治市|康登倫敦自治市]]。這裡是一個綜合用途地區，集合了居住、商業、零售、教育和醫療用地，並沒有一個突出的用途<ref>Matthew Sturgis, [http://www.thisislondon.co.uk/home/article-910971-all-the-fun-of-fitzrovia.do "All the fun of Fitzrovia"]{{dead link|date=十月 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}, ''Evening Standard'', 14 November 2001. Accessed 26 February 2011.</ref>。歷史上這裡是一個波希米亞地區，一些文化人如[[維吉尼亞·吳爾芙|維吉尼亞·吳爾芙]]、[[蕭伯納|蕭伯納]]和[[阿蒂爾·蘭波|阿蒂爾·蘭波]]曾在此居住。菲茨羅維亞是倫敦最富裕的地區之一<ref>Rees, Linus, [http://news.fitzrovia.org.uk/2011/02/17/fitzrovia-guy-ritchie-the-really-free-school-and-contempt-for-the-media/ "Fitzrovia, Guy Ritchie, The Really Free School, and contempt for the media"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.fitzrovia.org.uk/2011/02/17/fitzrovia-guy-ritchie-the-really-free-school-and-contempt-for-the-media/ |date=20160319025533 }}, ''Fitzrovia News'', 17 February 2011. Accessed 20 February 2011.</ref><ref>Penny, Laurie, [http://www.newstatesman.com/blogs/laurie-penny/2011/02/private-property-space-free "In defence of squatting"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.newstatesman.com/blogs/laurie-penny/2011/02/private-property-space-free |date=20170729132021 }}, ''New Statesman'', 20 February 2011. Accessed 20 February 2011.</ref>。[[英國電信塔|英國電信塔]]位於這裡。
